{"id":1340,"date":"2024-08-04T20:33:57","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T20:33:57","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1340"},"modified":"2024-09-17T21:51:07","modified_gmt":"2024-09-17T21:51:07","slug":"mission-058","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-058\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #058: Sweet Pie"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #058: Sweet Pie<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Blizzard City, Northeast House &#8211; Piemaker inside kitchen<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete the main story missions up until Blizzard City<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Give the Piemaker 1 Pecha Berry, 1 Qualot Berry and 1 Fresh Water.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>5 Hyper Potions<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>An elderly woman in Blizzard City loves making pies, and she needs the ingredients to make one for a birthday party. If you give her a Pecha Berry, a Qualot Berry, and a Fresh Water, she\u2019ll give you 5 Hyper Potions. This also leads to more pie quests.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>Go to the house right next to the entrance to the KBT Expressway in Blizzard City, in the northeast corner of town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-piemakers-house.jpg\" alt=\"The Piemaker\u2019s house \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Piemaker\u2019s house<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-ingredients-for-the-1st-pie.jpg\" alt=\"The ingredients for the first pie \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ingredients for the first pie<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The old lady inside this house is the Piemaker, and she wants to make a series of three pies, with a mission for each one.<\/p>\n<p>The first pie she wants to bake requires:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>1 Pecha Berry<\/li>\n<li>1 Qualot Berry<\/li>\n<li>1 Fresh Water<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-berry-pouch.jpg\" alt=\"The Berry Pouch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Berry Pouch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The ingredients can be found all over Borrius, but you can check our <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/items\/berries\/\">berries page<\/a> if you wanted more.<\/p>\n<p>Repeatable and reliable sources for these specific items are listed below:<\/p>\n<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" class=\"text-large center\">Ingredient Sources<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pecha&nbsp;Berry<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n        <strong>Route 7<\/strong><br \/>\n        Pecha Berries can be found as held items from Buneary caught on Route 7 &#8211; use Thief, Knock Off, Covet, or just capture the Buneary.\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/04-pokemon-unbound-route-7.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Qualot Berry<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n        <strong>Fallshore City<\/strong><br \/>\n        Qualot Berries can be bought at the northeast stall of the Fallshore City Market\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/05-pokemon-unbound-fallshore-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Fresh Water<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n        <strong>Dehara City<\/strong><br \/>\n        The \u201chuman vending machine\u201d on 6F of the Dehara City Department Store sells Fresh Water.\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/058\/06-pokemon-unbound-dehara-city.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>For giving her the ingredients for the first pie, the Piemaker gives you 5 Hyper Potions.<\/p>\n<p>You\u2019ll get the next mission in the series automatically &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-035\/\">Mission #035: Juicy Pie<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1341,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1340","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1340","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1341"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1340"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1340"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}